## 🚧 Known Issues

Cosmic AI is still in active development. You might run into bugs, especially on mobile. 

**Mobile issues we’re aware of:**
- Model loading can fail on some iOS/Android browsers
- UI scaling bugs on small screens  
- WebLLM crashes if you tab away too long

**If Cosmic AI isn’t working for you:**
1. Try desktop Chrome/Edge first — it’s the most stable
2. Clear site data + reload if models get stuck
3. Still broken? Join our Discord and drop a bug report: https://discord.gg/MGcayrSDzw

We push fixes constantly. V34.1.1 just shipped Meta theme + null safety patches.

